;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 304002004-->)
:{{DIcon}} I need your help to translate a slate.
::'''Mydei:''' Let me see.
::'''Mydei:''' ...
::'''Mydei:''' ...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Say something!
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504016215-->
::'''Mydei:''' Where did you find this slate? Castrum Kremnos?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What does the slate say?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504016217-->
::'''Mydei:''' Just some stories of the past, take a look for yourself. Come to think of it, did you not receive the benediction of Oronyx?
::'''Mydei:''' If you're interested, why not take a look around Castrum Kremnos for yourself? Maybe you will be able to dig up some interesting stories from among the dust of memories.
::Though you have more questions you want to ask, Mydei turns away and remains silent on the topic.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 304002004-->)
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Sorry. I'll be gone.
::'''Mydei:''' Farewell.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Mission_304003022-->
;(Unused &mdash; TalkSentence_504016126)
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504016126-->
::'''Mydei:''' ...Phainon is better suited for that than I am.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You two seem evenly matched.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504016128-->
:::'''Mydei:''' It is not merely martial strength that decides who will bear the Coreflame of Strife. Phainon... he is the flawless "Deliverer," and there is no greater candidate to inherit the divinity of Nikador.
:::'''Mydei:''' As long as he can overcome the fear in his heart, glory shall become his crown.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you scared that you would not pass the trial?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504016131-->
:::'''Mydei:''' Hmph. If a battle to the death with Nikador could not incite fear in my heart, what could scare me about a mere trial? The thing that stops me from grasping the Coreflame is not the trial of the Titan... but the trial of Castrum Kremnos.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504016132-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504016132-->
::'''Mydei:''' Allow me to interrupt your interrogation here. I have my own reasons for not accepting the Coreflame. I will not allow my decision to be shaken by your intentions. You may save your breath.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504016002_16-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504016002_16-->
